summary: An Ordinance providing for the cost and expense of the laying off, opening, extending and establishing of Twenty-fifth Avenue Northeast from Twenty-fifth Avenue Northeast, as established by deed, Ordinance No. 26504, to the north city limits, as a public street and highway, all in the City of Seattle, as provided in Ordinance No. 41606 of said city, by the issuance and sale of bonds of the district created to pay therefor.
